  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2668580/extras/df464362177c99a664813a693a7d0d99.avif?t=1699966877\" width=566 height=146 /></span><br><br> Cattie is a retro and challenging platform game where you control the lovely kitten Cattie through a series of challenging levels. With each level, the difficulty steadily increases, introducing new mechanics and enemies that will put your platforming skills to the test.<br><br><strong>Cattie's Abilities:</strong><br>Running, jumping, wall jumping, attacking, and crouching<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2668580/extras/e136125d61ff27fd8dd9fabdde8825e5.poster.avif?t=1699966877\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2668580/extras/e136125d61ff27fd8dd9fabdde8825e5.webm?t=1699966877\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2668580/extras/e136125d61ff27fd8dd9fabdde8825e5.mp4?t=1699966877\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>⮞ 100 Levels<br>⮞ 100 Achievements<br>⮞ 8-Bit Music",
